sentences: Jang Su-won (born July 16, 1980) is a South Korean singer.
He was in his second year of high school when he debuted as Sechs Kies in 1997.
In 2002, Su-won teamed with Kim Jae-duck to form J-Walk under Kiss Entertainment and began to sing more.
They took SBS Gayo Daejeon Popularity Award with Kang Sung-hun in 2002.
J-Walk released their third album My Love in 2008 and Eun Ji-won helped them by participating in the music video and featuring in the title song.
Su-won entered the military in December 2009 and served in Division 15's military band.
In September 2013, Su-won starred in the idol edition of "Love and War" but he was criticized for his poor acting, which has been labeled "robot-acting" and "unwatchable".
In 2014, people stopped criticizing him because of his nice attitude and good performance on the show Radio Star.
Su-won opened his own clothing line in the United States and provided uniforms for JYJ Kim Junsu's Hotel.
On June 12, 2021, Jang's agency announced that he and his non-celebrity girlfriend were planning their wedding.
1990s with Joon Park, Lee Ji-hye, EXID's Hyerin (Digital single from The Event King Of The Month), (2016)
